OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,FCriticising the Prime Minister, Mr
OL,8,FStreeting told Sky News' The Cathy
OL,9,FNewman Show: "I don't think he's
OL,10,Flistening to his former defence
OL,11,Fsecretary, I don't think he's
OL,12,Flistening to military chiefs, I don't
OL,13,Fthink he's listening to our Nato
OL,14,Fallies.
OL,26,@qD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,F"In terms of the Labour Party, I don't
OL,8,Fthink he's listening to his Cabinet, I
OL,9,Fdon't think he's listening to the
OL,10,Fparliamentary party and I don't think
OL,11,Fhe's listening to voters, who only in
OL,12,FMay sent the Labour Party that
OL,13,Fextremely humbling message at the
OL,14,Fballot box."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
