OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,FSpeaking to reporters earlier at a
OL,8,Fpress conference in central London
OL,9,Fwhere he outlined his economic vision,
OL,10,Fthe senior Labour figure said: "There
OL,11,Fis a huge amount of talent on the
OL,12,Ffront bench and the back bench of the
OL,13,Fparliamentary Labour Party.
OL,15,F"It isn't used nearly well enough, and
OL,16,Fthe divides between Labour's different
OL,17,Ftribes are often overstated.
OL,26,@rD@`OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,F"I think we all have a shared sense of
OL,8,Fwhat's wrong. I think we have
OL,9,Fdifferent views about how to put it
OL,10,Fright, but at the end of it, we need
OL,11,Fto come together."
OL,13,FMr Streeting's diagnosis is that
OL,14,FLabour is suffering from three
OL,15,Fproblems at the moment: with
OL,16,Fleadership, with policy, and with
OL,17,Fculture.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
