FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,FHe continued: "I would hope that after
OL,8,FThursday's by-election, when the
OL,9,Fresults are in, and I very much hope
OL,10,FAndy Burnham wins ` I was there
OL,11,Fyesterday campaigning for him again `
OL,12,Fwhen the results are in, I hope the
OL,13,FPrime Minister will at that stage
OL,14,Freflect on his own position and set
OL,15,Fout a timetable.
OL,17,F"I think that would be a better way
OL,18,Fforward for everyone, and would enable
OL,19,Fthat better culture that we aspire to."
OL,26,@oD@OOUyD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
