OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,FMeanwhile, former deputy prime
OL,8,Fminister Angela Rayner heaped praise
OL,9,Fon Mr Burnham's by-election campaign,
OL,10,Fsaying he was winning over voters with
OL,11,Fa "new type of politics" in an
OL,12,Finterview with the Mirror.
OL,14,FShe sidestepped questions on whether
OL,15,Fshe would back the Greater Manchester
OL,16,FMayor but said it was "hard to escape
OL,17,Fthe feeling that the public have had
OL,18,Ftowards Keir".
OL,26,@sD@COUsD@XO]xD@WOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
