FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,FAsked if it was too late to achieve
OL,8,Fthe change needed under Sir Keir's
OL,9,Fleadership, she said: "I don't think
OL,10,Fit's too late for the Labour Party to
OL,11,Fdeliver that, and that's a different
OL,12,Fquestion.
OL,14,F"I know I'm not answering your
OL,15,Fquestion direct. I think that it's
OL,16,Fhard to escape the feeling that the
OL,17,Fpublic have had towards Keir."
OL,19,FThe Prime Minister was asked about
OL,20,Fthreats to his leadership by reporters
OL,21,Fas he attended the G7 summit in France.
OL,26,@qD@WOUvD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
