PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,F"So very many times on my political
OL,8,Fjourney, people have said to me it's
OL,9,Fnot possible," he said.
OL,11,F"They said it's not possible to turn
OL,12,Fthe Labour Party around. It's not
OL,13,Fpossible to win an election.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@NO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,F"It's not possible if you do win
OL,8,Felection, to invest in your public
OL,9,Fservices and stabilise the economy `
OL,10,Fwrong every time, and that's why I
OL,11,Fintend not to walk away from this, but
OL,12,Fto carry on with what I was elected to
OL,13,Fdo, which is to serve this country,
OL,14,Fbring back the change that people
OL,15,Fdesperately need in their lives."
OL,17,FMr Burnham is the favourite to win the
OL,18,Fby-election in the Greater Manchester
OL,19,Fconstituency this week, multiple
OL,20,Fopinion polls have suggested.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
