OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781671666
OL,3,CStreeting prepared to trigger
OL,4,Cleadership contest as early as next
OL,5,Cweek
OL,7,FHis nearest challenger is Reform UK's
OL,8,FRobert Kenyon, though Nigel Farage's
OL,9,Fpolitical outfit is worried about
OL,10,Flosing voters to Restore Britain, a
OL,11,Fparty which positions itself as more
OL,12,Fhardline than Reform on migration and
OL,13,Fother issues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
